import './Education.css' const Education = () => { return (

Eductation

2018 - present

My Eduction

On this page you'll find my education jurney which started in March 2018. I started as a self tought dev, later taking a mobile app dev bootcamp in Android, that all together led me to start studying CS

Frontend

April 2018

Udemy Coure: Course

Completed half of this course, which includes the basics of Frontend; Html, CSS and basic Javascript. The course gave me the opportunity to code up my first few super basic projects

2021 - present

React

After studying CS and working oversees, I got back into shape and picked up React! Totally self learning, no course or anything

Native Android

2018 - 2019

John Bryce

Completed Successfully the Android Mobile App development course offered by John Bryce institution. On both Assigment I recieved 100/100

2018

Team Tree House

In order to supplement my education at John Bryce, I took upon myself to complete beginner Android tracks at Team Tree House

University

2019 - present

Open University of Israel

Currently pusuing a BSc in Computer Science, so far my GPA is 86. I play to complete the degree in early 2023

) } export default Education
